1. *Pošalji* mi poruku (Send me a message). 
2. On joj je *pošlao* pismo (He sent her a letter). 
3. Ona je *pošaljala* pisma preko interneta (She was sending letters online). 
4. Da li će ti on *poslati* email? (Will he send you an email?) 
5. *Pošalji* mi novčanik (Send me a wallet). 
6. Ona je *pošlala* svoju sliku (She sent her picture).